---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<main class="min-h-[70vh] bg-indigo-950 text-white -mb-1">
  <div
    class="flex h-full flex-col-reverse justify-center items-center xl:flex-row p-10 md:p-20 pt-10 xl:pt-36 xl:container xl:m-auto"
  >
    <div class="xl:w-[90%] flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h1 class="text-center text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-left">
        Turning Ideas into Interfaces  <br class="hidden md:block" />
        Problems into Products.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-center text-lg xl:text-left w-full leading-8">
        I’m Adam Olanrewaju — a full-stack developer passionate about clean
        architecture, efficient systems, and human-centered design. I build
        scalable backends, intuitive frontends, and smart automation tools that
        quietly solve real problems.
      </p>
      <p class="text-center text-lg xl:text-left w-full leading-8">
        Every project below tells its own story — of function, form, and the
        kind of software that gets things done.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/Adam-Olanrewaju-Resume.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="mt-2 px-5 py-5 bg-indigo-800 text-white rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors duration-200 w-fit self-center xl:self-start"
      >
        View Resume
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-full md:w-2/3">
      <Image
        width={800}
        height={800}
        alt="Showcase"
        class="w-full h-full"
        src={"/images/showcase.png"}
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
